{"id":36390,"date":"2021-05-30T10:49:29","date_gmt":"2021-05-30T06:49:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=36390"},"modified":"2023-08-31T21:02:01","modified_gmt":"2023-08-31T17:02:01","slug":"duha-better-than-spoils","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/duha-better-than-spoils\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Salat: Duha prayer better than spoils of war"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, once dispatched a company. They acquired spoils and rushed back to tell people how close their battle was, how many their spoils were, and how quickly they returned. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Shall I not tell you what is closer than a battle, more plentiful than spoils, and a swifter return? One who performs ablution, then goes to the mosque in the morning to glorify Allah in the forenoon. It is a closer battle, more plentiful spoils, and a swifter return.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6638<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0635\u0650\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064b \u0641\u064e\u063a\u064e\u0646\u0650\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u0